description.en:
Moonbar is a community-driven, fair-launched DeFi project built on Binance Smart Chain.
Moonbar presale will be launched on 07/06/2021 on dxSale

Three (3) mechanisms are activated during every transaction: 
- $MOONBAR Redestribution
- Liquidity Pool Acquisition
- $BNB Redestribution

By simply holding the token you get access to the community pool of $BNB AND earn more Moonbars!

$MOONBAR's mission is to truly become a decentralized project where every decision is taken by community poll. This helps the team to move $MOONBAR towards the right direction.
